data.description: This house is giving you all the things you need! Sitting on almost half an acre with a finished basement AND a garage. Beautiful hardwood floors throughout the main living room areas and updated kitchen + bathroom. Enjoy the large back yard and mature trees with a brand new wooden privacy fence. Basement area could be used as another bedroom or game room. Vivint security system offers 2 outdoor cameras, a doorbell camera, smart lock, door sensors, smart AC + carbon monoxide detector. This is a great home for a great price! Washer and dryer remains.
